{"tid":1236520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）立法會將辯論不信任第五屆香港特別行政區政府的議案","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T23:23:35.000Z","uid":97961,"like":178,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f3598a35c52b7aec7527f4076c3b4861b672a55d","tid":1236520,"uid":97961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"下稿代立法會秘書處發出:<br />\n<br />\n　　立法會將於星期三（六月十九日）上午十一時在立法會綜合大樓會議廳舉行會議。在會議上，郭榮鏗將動議一項議案，內容為：「本會不信任第五屆香港特別行政區政府。」<br />\n<br />\n　　毛孟靜將就郭榮鏗的議案提出修正案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/17/P2019061700785.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F17%2FP2019061700785.htm&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=7a092986\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/17/P2019061700785.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3cbdbf24f36cf27f045875b838f88a3c10ed3868","tid":1236520,"uid":5499,"like":52,"dislike":5,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"哂氣，咪又係比保皇保住"},{"pid":"f512a5cbbd59ca66e7434e72ad72b2340bb85b78","tid":1236520,"uid":226562,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"quote":{"pid":"3cbdbf24f36cf27f045875b838f88a3c10ed3868","tid":1236520,"uid":5499,"like":52,"dislike":5,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"哂氣，咪又係比保皇保住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:32:07.000Z","msg":"林鄭搞到好大單喎<br />\n分分鐘建制都要同埋發叔"},{"pid":"2ddc7f550ad887c9f69d949ad93d0fd3c3800aae","tid":1236520,"uid":28547,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"3cbdbf24f36cf27f045875b838f88a3c10ed3868","tid":1236520,"uid":5499,"like":52,"dislike":5,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"哂氣，咪又係比保皇保住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"歷史會有紀錄"},{"pid":"fe4ecb2c277761ab55c012005a93c432cde06026","tid":1236520,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"中央暫時都唔會畀林鄭落台